  "description": "A captivating seascape at dusk or dawn, featuring dark, turbulent waves crashing onto a black sand beach. The sky is a dramatic blend of deep blues and grays, hinting at an impending storm or the aftermath of one. The waves themselves are capped with white foam, creating a dynamic contrast against the dark water and shoreline. There's a subtle gradient of light on the horizon, suggesting the sun is either setting or rising, although obscured by the cloud cover. The overall composition evokes a sense of power and tranquility simultaneously.",
